OL,6,GThe BBC belongs to all of us. A
OL,7,Gstatement of the obvious, you might
OL,8,Gthink, but in a world of division that
OL,9,Gcan be a burden and not a blessing.
OL,11,FIt is very easy for us all to escape
OL,12,Finto the echo chambers of social media.
OL,13,FNo matter what your opinion or how
OL,14,Fniche your interests, you will find
OL,15,Fothers online who share your outlook.
OL,17,FIt might be a bit of harmless fun like
OL,18,Fnostalgia for old style Presentation or
OL,19,Fit could be a potentially harmful or
OL,20,Fextreme political opinion.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age of
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G1/10
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
