OL,6,FMark Chapman has told 5 Live listeners
OL,7,Fthat staff who worked on the station's
OL,8,Flimited sports coverage over the
OL,9,Fweekend received abuse. He says "there
OL,10,Fare lessons to be learned by all
OL,11,Finvolved". pic.twitter.com/Kly5emHU0N
OL,13,FFor a lot of people, the row over Gary
OL,14,FLineker's tweet seems to be a black and
OL,15,Fwhite issue.
OL,17,FTheir view of whether the BBC's initial
OL,18,Factions were appropriate depends
OL,19,Fentirely on whether they agreed with
OL,20,Fthe sentiments in the tweet.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age of
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G4/10
