OL,6,FMissing from this intemperate well of
OL,7,Fsocial media poison were two reasonable
OL,8,Fpositions which I suspect many people
OL,9,Fhold.
OL,11,
OL,12,F I agree with Gary but BBC Sport
OL,13,Fpresenters should not comment on issues
OL,14,Flike this publicly.
OL,15,F I don't agree with Gary but he has a
OL,16,Fperfect right to voice his views.
OL,18,FIf only a few more people realised
OL,19,Fthere were shades of grey.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age of
OL,4,Csocial media
