OL,6,FI say hopefully because there are
OL,7,Fundoubtedly grey areas. Not least the
OL,8,Fquestion of those freelance presenters
OL,9,Fwho are principally associated with key
OL,10,FBBC output.
OL,12,FBut there is nothing new. Thirty five
OL,13,Fyears ago, David Icke somehow managed
OL,14,Fto combine being a BBC Sport presenter
OL,15,Fwith being a Green Party spokesman.
OL,16,F(This was before his notorious
OL,17,Fappearance on Wogan and all which
OL,18,Ffollowed.)
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age of
OL,4,Csocial media
