OL,6,FAnd can you imagine having a regular
OL,7,Fcontributor to children's programmes
OL,8,Fwith right wing views which went well
OL,9,Fbeyond mainstream Conservative
OL,10,Fpolitics? Well did anyone suggest
OL,11,FNorris McWhirter should have been taken
OL,12,Foff Record Breakers in the 70s and
OL,13,Fearly 80s?
OL,15,FThankfully though this was before
OL,16,Fsocial media.
OL,18,FPerhaps this is a timely reminder. The
OL,19,Fcurrent problem facing the BBC is an
OL,20,Fage old one but one which poses
OL,21,Fdifferent challenges in an online age.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age of
OL,4,Csocial media
